      <title>特朗普暂缓发起贸易战，达沃斯论坛喘息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/davos-seeing-raft-of-trump-unknowns-counsels-calm-and-caution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，唐纳德·特朗普总统上任第一天只谈论贸易战而没有挑起贸易战，这让达沃斯的全球精英们松了一口气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/davos-seeing-raft-of-trump-unknowns-counsels-calm-and-caution</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 17:14:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非总统拉马福萨概述了担任 G20 主席国的愿景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/south-africa-s-ramaphosa-outlines-g-20-presidency-vision-at-wef</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统拉马福萨表示，南非将利用二十国集团主席国地位促进全球团结合作，解决发展中国家过重债务负担，加大应对气候变化力度，推进“绿色工业化”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/south-africa-s-ramaphosa-outlines-g-20-presidency-vision-at-wef</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 16:05:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>格陵兰总理希望与特朗普进行直接会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/greenland-premier-wants-direct-talks-with-trump-amid-interest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格陵兰总理表示，美国总统加大对丹麦施压，要求其移交北极岛屿的控制权，他希望与唐纳德·特朗普政府直接沟通。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/greenland-premier-wants-direct-talks-with-trump-amid-interest</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:51:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西政府反击虚假新闻威胁总统卢拉声望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/brazil-government-hits-back-against-fake-news-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西政府正在准备开展一项运动，以反击有关流行即时支付系统的虚假新闻的传播，这些新闻损害了总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦的声誉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/brazil-government-hits-back-against-fake-news-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:50:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官阻止司法部分享特朗普文件案报告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/judge-blocks-doj-from-sharing-report-on-trump-documents-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佛罗里达州一名联邦法官裁定，美国司法部不能与国会议员分享前特别顾问杰克·史密斯关于对唐纳德·特朗普总统的刑事调查报告的密封部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/judge-blocks-doj-from-sharing-report-on-trump-documents-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:39:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普暗示即将加征关税，加元接近新冠疫情时期低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/loonie-nears-covid-era-low-as-trump-signals-looming-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示将很快对美国邻国征收关税，随后加元跌至近五年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/loonie-nears-covid-era-low-as-trump-signals-looming-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:31:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多称特朗普的关税举措意在制造混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-s-tariff-whiplash-is-designed-to-sow-chaos-trudeau-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多表示，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普正试图在其贸易伙伴中制造不确定性，以使他们失去平衡并削弱他们的谈判地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-s-tariff-whiplash-is-designed-to-sow-chaos-trudeau-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:30:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨称欧盟正在制定全欧盟范围的电动汽车激励计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/scholz-says-eu-prepares-bloc-wide-purchase-premiums-for-evs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨周二表示，欧盟正在制定一项在欧盟范围内实施电动汽车购买激励措施的提案，以支持欧盟陷入困境的汽车制造商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/scholz-says-eu-prepares-bloc-wide-purchase-premiums-for-evs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:14:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普让比索暴跌，Sheinbaum 呼吁“保持冷静”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/mexico-must-keep-cool-head-on-trump-orders-sheinbaum-says-m66jyfvz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普誓言要征收高额关税，导致墨西哥货币因担心墨西哥将成为其政府的目标而暴跌，总统克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆呼吁民众保持冷静。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/mexico-must-keep-cool-head-on-trump-orders-sheinbaum-says-m66jyfvz</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 14:10:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普行政措施概述，从关税到移民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/trump-executive-orders-tariffs-immigration-energy-among-top-priorities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一就职典礼后，唐纳德·特朗普总统立即兑现了他的许多竞选承诺，包括关于移民、能源、军事和联邦劳动力等方面的承诺，其中许多承诺被认为推翻了他的前任乔·拜登的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/trump-executive-orders-tariffs-immigration-energy-among-top-priorities</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 21:12:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
